OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783963264
OL,3,CTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man found seriously
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FTwo men have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of murder after a man was
OL,9,Ffound seriously injured in Leicester.
OL,11,FThe man in his late 20s was found by
OL,12,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service in
OL,13,FCompton Road in the early hours of the
OL,14,Fmorning on Sunday, 12 July. He was
OL,15,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,17,FTwo men, aged 36 and 27, were arrested
OL,18,Fand remain in police custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783963264
OL,3,CTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man found seriously
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FForensic officers were seen working at
OL,8,Fthe scene throughout the day, with a
OL,9,Fblue police tent erected within the
OL,10,Fcordon earlier on Sunday morning.
OL,12,FThe tent has since been taken down,
OL,13,Fthough the cordon and privacy screens
OL,14,Fremain in place in Compton Road, near
OL,15,FNarborough Road.
OL,17,FAn investigation was launched to
OL,18,Festablish how the man came to be in
OL,19,Fthe street and the full circumstances
OL,20,Fof what happened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783963264
OL,3,CTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man found seriously
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,FThe man's next of kin have been
OL,8,Fidentified and are being supported by
OL,9,Ftrained officers.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Kevin Hames, from
OL,12,Fthe East Midlands Special Operations
OL,13,FUnit, said: "We are in the very early
OL,14,Fstages of this investigation, with
OL,15,Ffull enquiries being carried out as we
OL,16,Fcontinue to establish what has
OL,17,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783963264
OL,3,CTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man found seriously
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,F"As we progress our enquiries, I do of
OL,8,Fcourse ask that anyone with any
OL,9,Finformation makes contact with us as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible.
OL,12,F"Were you in the area of Compton Road
OL,13,Fthis morning? Did you see or hear
OL,14,Fanything which caused you concern?
OL,16,F"I would also ask anyone with CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage or dashcam footage from the
OL,18,Farea to get in touch.J"Further
OL,19,Fenquiries including speaking with
OL,20,Fwitnesses, CCTV analysis and forensic
OL,21,Fexamination is ongoing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783963264
OL,3,CTwo men arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after man found seriously
OL,5,Cinjured
OL,7,F"We also have officers in the area and
OL,8,Fat the scene. We understand the
OL,9,Fconcern this incident may cause so
OL,10,Fplease do speak to officers in the
OL,11,Farea about any information or concerns
OL,12,Fyou may have.
OL,14,F"A major Incident Public Portal has
OL,15,Fbeen opened and I would ask anyone
OL,16,Fwith any information to make contact
OL,17,Fwith us as soon as possible."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
